quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  26,53,Tokkel firqawni kay reedah gubaak tan magaaloolih qaskar ruube macaxu kaah kobxisaanamkeh israa-iil xaylok mawuq yoobbe waqdi
  26,54,"Firqawni: diggah a-mari (israa-iil xaylo kinnuk) dago horta iyye"
  26,55,Kaadu diggah usun kaxxam nee ceerissa taama aben
  26,56,"Diggah nanu inkih cibbarsimaah, gulguluh keenih yan mara kinnino iyye"
  26,57,Firqawnaa kee kay mara Masri baaxoy basaatin kee daroori-lek ken neyyeeqeh
  26,58,Kaadu kadnoonii kee meqe aroocaay meqe qarwak ken neyyeeqe
  26,59,"Too mayyuq keenit kah abne innah, kaadu ken dabooqaa kee ken maalu israa-iil xaylo nagarsisne ken bayisneek gamadal"
  26,60,Tokkel firqawnaa kee kay macaxi Nabii Muusaa kee kaâ luk yan mara ayro edde tawqe waktit kataaten
  26,61,"Tokkel namma butta (firqawni maraa kee Muusâ mara kinnuk) sitta tuble waqdi, Nabii Muusâ kataysis:diggah nanu elel simneeh firqwnaa kee kay macxi nee qide-le iyyen"
  26,62,"Nabii Muusa keenik iyyeh: aleey, sin meeleelan, diggah anu yoo qokla Rabbi liyooh, edde naggoowa gita yoh ascasse-le"
  26,63,"Tokkel Nabii Muusal isi caxxat bad atuk iyyaanamah wacyi kaal oobisne, tokkel usuk kaa yootokeeh, bad baxsimeeh kulli exxa kaak kaxxa qaleh innah gacca itte"
  26,64,Kaadu tokkel aka mara xayyosne (firqawnaa kee kay mara kinnuk) badat cullu iyyaanam fanah Muusaa kee Muusâ marih lakal
  26,65,Kaadu Nabii Muusaa kee kaâ luk yan mara inkih naggosneh
  26,66,Tohuk lakal aka mara badat xuumusne (firqawnaa kee kay macaxu kinnuk)
  26,67,"Diggah tohut Yallih inkittinaanee kee kay dudda tascasse astá tan, kaadu keenik maggo mari yeemene mara makkinna"
  26,68,"Kaadu diggah ku-Rabbi, usuk maysoli xuwawli kinni"
  26,69,Kaadu Nabiyow ama korosul Nabii Ibraahim xaagu maaqaay keenil akriy